{
  "description": "jCodeMunch repo ids and best-of entry points for external skill repos. Use search_symbols(repo, query) / get_symbol(repo, ...) with these repo ids. Paths from OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_SKILLS or ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills.",
